https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500null No aspect of island culture is safe from Da Braddahs' wacky brand of Hawaiian-style ridicule on their popular self-produced sketch comedy TV series. In Volume 5, Da Braddahs -- aka James Roche and Tony Silva -- assume the personas of McGariff and Danko of Westside 5-O to bring down the "Super Sugar Mafiosis" -- a mission that takes them deep into the heart of Chinatown to track down the uncle of the island's biggest go-go dancer booking agency.
